bm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173170/extras/296d9c80c5da5e5d7b213c736c22d555.mp4?t=1728090256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Regenerate nearby items</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173170/extras/806d7dc523ecf0ec648e931f98824523.poster.avif?t=1728090256\" width=580 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173170/extras/806d7dc523ecf0ec648e931f98824523.webm?t=1728090256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173170/extras/806d7dc523ecf0ec648e931f98824523.mp4?t=1728090256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Base material for tributing</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173170/extras/f55a391ce0ebc748e2e8e521f35eb8df.poster.avif?t=1728090256\" width=450 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173170/extras/f55a391ce0ebc748e2e8e521f35eb8df.webm?t=1728090256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2173170/extras/f55a391ce0ebc748e2e8e521f35eb8df.mp4?t=1728090256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Unlock weapons to destroy scenario items such as (trees, columns, scaffolds, blocks, and enemies)<br></li><li> Unlock shield to defense by enemy attack and dodge blocks to solve single puzzles<br></li><li> Collect materials such as (wood, stone, and metal) for crafting(weapons and shields) and advance in the map <br></li><li> Regenerate raw materials through the map (tree, column, scaffold, blocks) and keep gameplay self-sufficient<br></li><li> A tribute system, exchanging part of life by materials, and vice-versa<br></li><li> A secret menu in <i>pause game</i> to set some cheats</li></ul>",
